176 A.3d 213 STATE OF NEW JERSEY, PLAINTIFF, v. KENNETH B. GREEN, DEFENDANT; STATE OF NEW JERSEY, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. LOUIS ADAMS, DEFENDANT-PETITIONER.

C-370 September Term 2017

079114 November 30, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-2342/3251-13 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
